      <hedline>
        <hl1>Correction</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Correction of photograph with May 27 travel article about summer music festivals in Tuscany (S)</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>A photograph with the In Transit column on May 27 about summer music festivals in Tuscany was published in error. It depicted the fortress at Montalcino, not the villa La Foce, which is the site for much of the Incontri in Terra di Siena festival.</p>
      </block>
      <block class="full_text">
